title: Trump says he will cancel all Biden executive orders signed by autopen – live
summary: The US president intensified efforts to depict his predecessor as incapable and disconnected from reality through a recent social media post. title: Former Ukip MEP denies taking money to promote Russian interests
summary: David Coburn, former leader of Ukip in Scotland, has denied any involvement following the sentencing of Nathan Gill, who was imprisoned for accepting bribes. Coburn's statement comes as the party faces scrutiny over Gill's actions. The situation raises concerns about ethical practices within the party.

title: Woman jailed for harassing Rachel Reeves’ sister
summary: Tracey Smith communicated with government minister and MP Ellie Reeves by sending 22 emails and leaving 10 voicemails. The details surrounding the content and purpose of these messages are not specified. The correspondence highlights Smith's efforts to engage with the MP.
